flowchart TD
    %% title: Chapter 4: Control Flow Decision Tree
    
    Start([Start]) --> IfCheck{if condition}
    
    IfCheck -->|true| IfBlock[Execute if block]
    IfCheck -->|false| ElseCheck{else if?}
    
    ElseCheck -->|true| ElseIfBlock[Execute else if block]
    ElseCheck -->|false| ElseBlock[Execute else block]
    
    IfBlock --> MatchExpr{match value}
    ElseIfBlock --> MatchExpr
    ElseBlock --> MatchExpr
    
    MatchExpr -->|pattern 1| Action1[Execute arm 1]
    MatchExpr -->|pattern 2| Action2[Execute arm 2]
    MatchExpr -->|pattern n| ActionN[Execute arm n]
    MatchExpr -->|_ wildcard| Default[Execute default arm]
    
    Action1 --> Loop{loop type?}
    Action2 --> Loop
    ActionN --> Loop
    Default --> Loop
    
    Loop -->|loop| LoopInf[infinite loop]
    Loop -->|while| LoopWhile[while condition]
    Loop -->|for| LoopFor[for item in iterator]
    
    LoopInf --> LoopBody[Execute body]
    LoopWhile -->|true| LoopBody
    LoopFor --> LoopBody
    
    LoopBody --> Break{break?}
    Break -->|yes| End([End])
    Break -->|no| Continue{continue?}
    
    Continue -->|yes| Loop
    Continue -->|no| LoopBody
    
    LoopWhenFalse --> End
    
    style Start fill:#b2f2bb
    style End fill:#b2f2bb
    style IfCheck fill:#fef3c7
    style ElseCheck fill:#fef3c7
    style MatchExpr fill:#fef3c7
    style Loop fill:#fef3c7
    style Break fill:#fef3c7
